text:
We will now start the test portion

Please judge the number on magnitude (higher or lower than 5) or parity (odd or even), depending on which quadrant the numbers are in.

In the top two quadrants, please judge the number based on magnitude. Press the M Key if high, and the Z Key if low.

In the bottom two quadrants, please judge the number based on parity. Press the M Key if even, and the Z Key if odd.

On some trials, you will see a star appear at the same time, or shortly after, the number. Do not respond if you see a star. Do not slow down your responses in order to wait for the star.

You will no longer receive the rule prompt, so remember the instructions before you continue. Press Enter to begin.
